creator: Tysoft Software Ltd
descriptionHtml:
EasyPAT Mobile works with the EasyPAT desktop software to record and input all results direct onto your phone to be then imported into your desktop software.

EasyPAT Mobile saves time and effort by not having to write certificates by hand onsite. You only need to input the information once and you are set. The powerful EasyPAT Mobile wizards walk you through each part of the certificate allowing you to enter the information as you go.

On completion of reports you simply upload certificates over your devices data connection, which can then be instantly downloaded direct into the EasyPAT desktop software. There is no messing around connecting your phone to your computer as everything is wireless making it quick and easy.
descriptionShort: EasyPAT Mobile for recording and printing portable appliance testing reports!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Includes many small improvements and fixes.
